26 SECTION 1. DO NOT CODIFY. Legislative findings.
27 The General Assembly finds that:
28 (1) A citizen of this state may receive potable water through a
29 lead service line;
30 (2) Lead may detach from a lead service line and contaminate
31 water that moves through the lead service line;
32 (3) Lead exposure may cause:
33 (A) Organ damage, including without limitation brain
34 damage, kidney damage, heart damage, and lung damage;
35 (B) Diminution in bone mass and muscle growth;
36 (C) Poor muscle coordination;
