14 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code Title 14, Chapter 234, Subchapter 1, is
15 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
16 § 14-234-123. Replacement of lead service lines —— Issuance of bonds
17 —— Definitions.
18 (a) As used in this section:
19 (1) "Lead service line" means a water service line that is
20 constructed of:
21 (A) Lead, at least in part; or
22 (B) Galvanized steel and exists or previously existed
23 downstream of a service line or other conduit constructed of lead material or
24 unknown material;
25 (2) "Person" means:
26 (A) A public or private corporation;
27 (B) An individual;
28 (C) A partnership;
29 (D) An association; or
30 (E) Other entity;
31 (3) "Public entity" means:
32 (A) A municipality;
33 (B) A consolidated waterworks system as defined in § 25-
34 20-307;
35 (C) A water authority as defined in § 4-35-103;
36 (D) A public facilities board as defined in § 14-137-103;
