15 that the water provider serves; and
16 (2) Use existing statutory authority that permits the water
17 provider to issue bonds for waterworks system improvements to:
18 (A) Issue bonds; and
19 (B) Use the proceeds to replace a lead service line of a
20 customer that the water provider serves.
21 (d) A water provider replacing a lead service line that another person
22 owns does not confer ownership or maintenance responsibilities for the
23 replaced lead service line on the water provider unless the water provider
24 and other person otherwise agree.
